        ║  SAGE CONSTELLATION — 56 Nodes, 5 Branches          ║
        ║  Layout: X-cross — Scholar(NW) / Mindkeeper(NE) /   ║
        ║          Empath(SW) / Physician(SE) + Ascetic(N)    ║
