    <IsekaiLeveling.SkillTree.PassiveTreeDef>
        <defName>PassiveTree_Sage</defName>
        <label>Sage</label>
        <treeClass>Sage</treeClass>
        <treeDescription>Masters of mind and medicine, Sages channel wisdom into healing, knowledge, and unshakeable mental clarity. Five constellations radiate from the sage's quiet core — each refining the art of supporting and understanding. Keep the battlefield at bay: silence restores the Sage's deepest gifts through Inner Calm.</treeDescription>
        <classGimmick>InnerCalm</classGimmick>
        <classGimmickName>Inner Calm</classGimmickName>
        <classGimmickDescription>The longer a Sage goes without taking damage, the more their clarity of mind amplifies their healing and research. Any hostile hit resets the calm timer entirely. Inner Calm scales along the Ascetic Path. Tier 1 (Tranquil Mind): calm builds over 4 in-game hours → up to +20% TendQuality and SurgerySuccess, +10% Research. Tier 2 (Serene Focus): builds over 3 hours → up to +35% / +18%. Tier 3 (Sage's Peace): builds over 2 hours → up to +55% / +28%. Tier 4 (Perfect Stillness): builds over 1 hour → up to +80% / +40%. Scales linearly — maximum bonus at full calm duration.</classGimmickDescription>

